@wip
Feature: View all job application statuses
    As a student 
    View different application statuses on job dashboard
    And interact with applications through dashboard  

Background:
    Given the student user is logged into the system
    And viewing the Job Search section
    And viewing the JOb Tracker dashboard

@wip
Scenario Outline: Postings are visible for each category of application status
    Given the student user is viewing the 'Job Tracker'
    Then the system presents six application status category tabs: "Bookmarked", "Applied", "Interviewing", "Negotiating", "Not Selected", and "No Response"
    When the student user selects the category button
    Then only jobs with that status are displayed in dashboard

    Examples:
        | Status       |
        | Bookmarked   |
        | Applied      |
        | Interviewing |
        | Negotiating  |
        | Not Selected |
        | No Response  |
